  "description": "<b>感谢<a href=\"http://bbs.feball.com\" target=\"_blank\">ball</a>的投递</b><br /> 上个月初的时候外媒&#160;AppleInsider&#160;曾报道，在一次内部全体员工大会上，苹果通知全体技术人员：苹果还将扩大售后服务范围，降低成本。做为“扩大服务范围，降低成本”计划的一部分，苹果今天正式开始在零售店内提供&#160;iPhone&#160;5&#160;屏幕更换服务，服务价格为&#160;149&#160;美元，有无&#160;AppleCare+&#160;均可以享受。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ccb0fde/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239754.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%BA%97iPhone+5%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%9B%B4%E6%8D%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239754.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%BA%97iPhone+5%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%9B%B4%E6%8D%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239754.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%BA%97iPhone+5%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%9B%B4%E6%8D%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239754.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%BA%97iPhone+5%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%9B%B4%E6%8D%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=htt